:getMessage)\n              .collect(Collectors.toList());\n      throw new ModelValidationException(messages);\n    }\n\n    return model;\n  }\n}\n```"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dc68c8b7-f26e-40c7-b046-67d783731ba6","uuid":"a1a00a70-addd-49dc-9c1b-30e010a0870e"}
