 = findTagEntityById(tagRelationship.getTag().getId());\n    29→        entityManager.persist(new TagRelationshipEntity(articleEntity, tagEntity));\n    30→    }\n    31→\n    32→    @Override\n    33→    public List<Tag> findArticleTags(Article article) {\n    34→        return entityManager.createQuery(\n    35→                        \"from TagRelationshipEntity as tagRelationship where tagRelationship.primaryKey.article.id = :articleId\",\n    36→                        TagRelationshipEntity.class)\n    37→                .setParameter(\"articleId\", article.getId())\n    38→                .getResultList()\n    39→                .stream()\n    40→                .map(entityUtils::tag)\n    41→                .collect(Collectors.toList());\n    42→    }\n    43→}\n    44→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01YAAD7Xs6gL4qHbtHcnyzbG","session_id":"dc68c8b7-f26e-40c7-b046-67d783731ba6","uuid":"1e4085de-9f20-48a0-88f3-00f41874aa45"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01YAAD7Xs6gL4qHbtHcnyzbG","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully migrated all 8 Panache repository implementations to Spring Data JPA / EntityManager based implementations. Here's a summary of the changes:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\n### All 8 Files Successfully Written:\n\n1. **AbstractPanacheRepository.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/AbstractPanacheRepository.java`\n   - Removed Quarkus `PanacheRepositoryBase` interface\n   - Added `@PersistenceContext` EntityManager injection\n   - Replaced `getEntityManager()` calls with direct `entityManager` usage\n\n2. **ArticleRepositoryPanache.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/ArticleRepositoryPanache.java`\n   - Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n   - Removed `@AllArgsConstructor`, added explicit constructor\n   - Converted Panache methods to EntityManager JPQL queries\n   - Replaced `count()`, `find()`, `persistAndFlush()`, `deleteById()` with EntityManager equivalents\n\n3. **UserRepositoryPanache.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/UserRepositoryPanache.java`\n   - Replaced `persist()` with `entityManager.persist()`\n   - Converted Panache queries to JPQL with EntityManager\n   - Updated `update()` method to use `entityManager.merge()`\n\n4. **CommentRepositoryPanache.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/CommentRepositoryPanache.java`\n   - Converted all Panache finder methods to EntityManager queries\n   - Replaced `delete()` with `entityManager.remove()` with null checks\n\n5. **TagRepositoryPanache.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/TagRepositoryPanache.java`\n   - Replaced `listAll()` with `entityManager.createQuery()`\n   - Converted all queries to standard JPQL\n\n6. **FavoriteRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/FavoriteRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java`\n   - Converted composite key lookups to EntityManager queries\n   - Added null checks for delete operations\n\n7. **FollowRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/FollowRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java`\n   - Converted Panache `find(\"primaryKey\", ...)` to `entityManager.find()` with composite key\n   - Updated all query methods to use EntityManager\n\n8. **TagRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/TagRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java`\n   - Converted to standard JPQL queries with EntityManager\n\n### Key Changes Made:\n- **Removed Quarkus dependencies**: No more `io.quarkus.*` imports\n- **Added Spring annotations**: `@Repository` instead of `@ApplicationScoped`\n- **EntityManager injection**: Using `@PersistenceContext` for Spring-managed EntityManager\n- **Direct JPQL queries**: All Panache convenience methods replaced with explicit `createQuery()` calls\n- **Explicit transaction handling**: Using `entityManager.flush()` and `entityManager.merge()` where needed\n- **Null safety**: Added null checks before `entityManager.remove()` operations\n\nAll files have been successfully migrated from Quarkus Panache to Spring Data JPA with EntityManager."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dc68c8b7-f26e-40c7-b046-67d783731ba6","uuid":"dff00a88-cd6b-4c7a-83b9-e7fb8b3d7f9b"}
