{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WuPJyEz9UcHLwWhQ8qhiyW","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully updated all the requested files. Let me provide you with a detailed summary of the changes made.\n\n## Migration Complete: Quarkus to Spring Boot Exception Handling and Annotations\n\nI have successfully migrated the exception handling and removed Quarkus-specific annotations from your RealWorld API project. Here's a detailed breakdown of all changes:\n\n### 1. Exception Handler (ExceptionMappers.java)\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/mapper/ExceptionMappers.java`\n\n**Key Changes:**\n- Replaced `@ServerExceptionMapper` with `@ExceptionHandler` annotations\n- Added `@RestControllerAdvice` at class level\n- Replaced `Response` with `ResponseEntity<ErrorResponse>`\n- Replaced `Response.Status` with Spring's `HttpStatus`\n- Updated exception handling for `BadCredentialsException` and `AccessDeniedException` (Spring Security exceptions)\n- Added handlers for `ConstraintViolationException` and `MethodArgumentNotValidException`\n\n### 2. Bean Validation Exception Mapper\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/mapper/BeanValidationExceptionMapper.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced content with a comment noting it's no longer needed\n- Exception handling now consolidated in `ExceptionMappers.java` via `@RestControllerAdvice`\n\n### 3. EntityUtils.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/entity/EntityUtils.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Component`\n- Changed import from `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped` to `org.springframework.stereotype.Component`\n\n### 4. Request Models (Removed @RegisterForReflection)\nAll request models have been updated to remove the Quarkus-specific `@RegisterForReflection` annotation:\n\n- **LoginRequest.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/request/LoginRequest.java`\n- **NewArticleRequest.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/request/NewArticleRequest.java`\n- **NewCommentRequest.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/request/NewCommentRequest.java`\n- **NewUserRequest.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/request/NewUserRequest.java`\n- **UpdateArticleRequest.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/request/UpdateArticleRequest.java`\n- **UpdateUserRequest.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/request/UpdateUserRequest.java`\n\n### 5. Response Models (Removed @RegisterForReflection)\nAll response models have been updated to remove the Quarkus-specific `@RegisterForReflection` annotation:\n\n- **ArticleResponse.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/response/ArticleResponse.java`\n- **ArticlesResponse.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/response/ArticlesResponse.java`\n- **CommentResponse.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/response/CommentResponse.java`\n- **CommentsResponse.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/response/CommentsResponse.java`\n- **ErrorResponse.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/response/ErrorResponse.java`\n- **ProfileResponse.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/response/ProfileResponse.java`\n- **TagsResponse.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/response/TagsResponse.java`\n- **UserResponse.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/response/UserResponse.java`\n\n### Summary of Changes:\n- **15 files** updated in total\n- Removed all Quarkus-specific annotations (`@RegisterForReflection`, `@ApplicationScoped`, `@ServerExceptionMapper`, `@Provider`)\n- Replaced with Spring equivalents (`@Component`, `@RestControllerAdvice`, `@ExceptionHandler`)\n- Updated exception handling to use Spring's `ResponseEntity` and `HttpStatus`\n- All validation constraints and business logic remain intact\n\nThe migration is now complete and your RealWorld API should be compatible with Spring Boot's exception handling and dependency injection mechanisms."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dc68c8b7-f26e-40c7-b046-67d783731ba6","uuid":"5d5e3bda-b7d0-4d5a-8a01-2f61d6e5117c"}
