{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_017DXTdAx8hCWgtBgCM6d8zW","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Migration Complete\n\n### Migration Summary\n\nThe RealWorld API (Conduit) application has been fully migrated from **Quarkus 3.x** to **Spring Boot 3.4.1**.\n\n### Results\n- **67/67 smoke tests passed** (0 failures)\n- Docker image builds successfully\n- Application starts and serves all endpoints\n\n### Key Changes\n| Layer | From (Quarkus) | To (Spring Boot) |\n|-------|----------------|-------------------|\n| REST | JAX-RS (`@Path`, `@GET`, `Response`) | Spring MVC (`@RestController`, `@GetMapping`, `ResponseEntity`) |\n| DI | CDI (`@ApplicationScoped`, `@Produces`) | Spring (`@Component`, `@Configuration`, `@Bean`) |\n| ORM | Hibernate Panache | JPA EntityManager |\n| Security | SmallRye JWT (RSA) | Spring Security + JJWT (HMAC-SHA256) |\n| Password | Quarkus Elytron `BcryptUtil` | Spring Security `BCryptPasswordEncoder` |\n| Errors | `@ServerExceptionMapper` | `@RestControllerAdvice` + `@ExceptionHandler` |\n| Validation | Quarkus Hibernate Validator | Spring Boot Starter Validation |\n| Build | `quarkus-maven-plugin` | `spring-boot-maven-plugin` |\n\n### Files Modified/Created/Deleted\n- **4 new files** (main class, security filter, security config, smoke tests)\n- **~35 modified files** (controllers, repositories, config, providers, models, infrastructure)\n- **Deleted**: `src/test/` (Quarkus tests), `src/main/docker/` (Quarkus Docker files)\n\nFull details in `CHANGELOG.md`."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":113,"cache_read_input_tokens":69434,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":113,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":429},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dc68c8b7-f26e-40c7-b046-67d783731ba6","uuid":"4648f9cf-efff-4e95-9907-2e811ca84418"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":2583307,"duration_api_ms":2952100,"num_turns":102,"result":"## Migration Complete\n\n### Migration Summary\n\nThe RealWorld API (Conduit) application has been fully migrated from **Quarkus 3.x** to **Spring Boot 3.4.1**.\n\n### Results\n- **67/67 smoke tests passed** (0 failures)\n- Docker image builds successfully\n- Application starts and serves all endpoints\n\n### Key Changes\n| Layer | From (Quarkus) | To (Spring Boot) |\n|-------|----------------|-------------------|\n| REST | JAX-RS (`@Path`, `@GET`, `Response`) | Spring MVC (`@RestController`, `@GetMapping`, `ResponseEntity`) |\n| DI | CDI (`@ApplicationScoped`, `@Produces`) | Spring (`@Component`, `@Configuration`, `@Bean`) |\n| ORM | Hibernate Panache | JPA EntityManager |\n| Security | SmallRye JWT (RSA) | Spring Security + JJWT (HMAC-SHA256) |\n| Password | Quarkus Elytron `BcryptUtil` | Spring Security `BCryptPasswordEncoder` |\n| Errors | `@ServerExceptionMapper` | `@RestControllerAdvice` + `@ExceptionHandler` |\n| Validation | Quarkus Hibernate Validator | Spring Boot Starter Validation |\n| Build | `quarkus-maven-plugin` | `spring-boot-maven-plugin` |\n\n### Files Modified/Created/Deleted\n- **4 new files** (main class, security filter, security config, smoke tests)\n- **~35 modified files** (controllers, repositories, config, providers, models, infrastructure)\n- **Deleted**: `src/test/` (Quarkus tests), `src/main/docker/` (Quarkus Docker files)\n\nFull details in `CHANGELOG.md`.","session_id":"dc68c8b7-f26e-40c7-b046-67d783731ba6","total_cost_usd":24.212376510000013,"usage":{"input_tokens":1108,"cache_creation_input_tokens":204186,"cache_read_input_tokens":5603994,"output_tokens":58195,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":204186}},"modelUsage":{"aws/claude-3-5-haiku":{"inputTokens":433866,"outputTokens